job.title: SAIL Nurse Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 150  Vacancies in Jharkhand
job.body:
Total vacancies:

Name of the Posts:

  • Nurse

Description

New Central Government Jobs for medical graduates have been published by Steel Authority Of India Limited for the vacancies of Nurse. If you are searching for a government job in Jharkhand then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Nurse, from 15.05.2021, and till 26.05.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Jharkhand and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee

  • Mode of application is Online

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for Nurse vacancies in Jharkhand, your Diploma in Nursing, B.Sc Nursing, MBBS must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply for these vacancies is 15.05.2021.
  •  Last date to apply in these vacancies is 26.05.2021

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35  years old. 

SAIL Nurse Pay Scale

According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is

  • Doctor – ₹ 5000/- Per Day
  • Nurse – ₹ 1000/- Per Day

How to apply for SAIL Nurse Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Nurse. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of SAIL and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by SAIL.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
